umpire method

UNDERSTAND

1. ask the interviewer "clarifying" questions before jumping to attempt the question.
2. take 2-3 minutes
3. think of edge cases(think of extreme cases)
4. these questions are moslty related to input

MATCH

1. does this problem match any common patterns we have seen.
2. which data structure to use

PLAN/PSUEDOCODE

1. use diagrams and psuedocode
2. run psuedocode with test cases

IMPLEMENT

1. Translate algorithm/psuedocode in to code

REVIEW

1. Run some test cases/Dry run and see if your test cases are successfully passed.

EVALUATE

1. Calculate time and space complexity
2. Think how your solution can be made more efficient
